<section id="servicos" class="py-20 lg:py-32">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-foreground sm:text-4xl">
        Meus Serviços
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-lg leading-8 text-muted-foreground">
        Ofereço soluções completas em desenvolvimento React com atenção
        personalizada ao seu projeto.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div
      class="mx-auto mt-16 grid max-w-2xl grid-cols-1 gap-8 sm:mt-20 lg:mx-0 lg:max-w-none lg:grid-cols-3"
    >
      <div
        class="flex flex-col gap-6 rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-8"
      >
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
          <div
            class="flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-primary/10"
          >
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              width="24"
              height="24"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              stroke-width="2"
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              class="h-6 w-6 text-primary"
            >
              <path d="m18 16 4-4-4-4"></path>
              <path d="m6 8-4 4 4 4"></path>
              <path d="m14.5 4-5 16"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-foreground">
            Desenvolvimento React
          </h3>
        </div>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground">
          Criamos aplicações React escaláveis e performáticas usando as melhores
          práticas e arquiteturas modernas.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div
        class="flex flex-col gap-6 rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-8"
      >
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
          <div
            class="flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-primary/10"
          >
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              width="24"
              height="24"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              stroke-width="2"
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              class="h-6 w-6 text-primary"
            >
              <path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-foreground">Next.js & SSR</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground">
          Implementamos soluções com Next.js para SEO otimizado, renderização
          server-side e performance excepcional.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div
        class="flex flex-col gap-6 rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-8"
      >
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
          <div
            class="flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-primary/10"
          >
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              width="24"
              height="24"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              stroke-width="2"
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              class="h-6 w-6 text-primary"
            >
              <path
                d="M12 2v20M17 5H9.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 0 7h5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 0 7H6"
              ></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-foreground">Design Systems</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground">
          Construímos componentes reutilizáveis e design systems completos para
          manter consistência em larga escala.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
